fields.title: Spaghetti Carbonara
fields.ingredients: Spaghetti, eggs, Parmesan cheese, pancetta, garlic, black pepper, salt.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook spaghetti. 2. Cook pancetta and garlic. 3. Mix eggs and cheese. 4. Combine all and serve.

fields.title: Chicken Curry
fields.ingredients: Chicken, curry powder, onion, garlic, ginger, coconut milk, tomatoes.
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté onion, garlic, and ginger. 2. Add chicken and curry powder. 3. Add tomatoes and coconut milk. 4. Simmer and serve.

fields.title: Caesar Salad
fields.ingredients: Romaine lettuce, Caesar dressing, croutons, Parmesan cheese.
fields.instructions: 1. Toss lettuce with dressing. 2. Add croutons and cheese. 3. Serve immediately.

fields.title: Beef Tacos
fields.ingredients: Ground beef, taco seasoning, tortillas, lettuce, cheese, salsa.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook beef with seasoning. 2. Fill tortillas with beef and toppings. 3. Serve with salsa.

fields.title: Vegetable Stir-Fry
fields.ingredients: Mixed vegetables, soy sauce, garlic, ginger, rice.
fields.instructions: 1. Stir-fry vegetables with garlic and ginger. 2. Add soy sauce. 3. Serve with rice.

fields.title: Chocolate Chip Cookies
fields.ingredients: Flour, sugar, butter, chocolate chips, eggs, baking soda.
fields.instructions: 1. Mix ingredients. 2. Form into balls and bake. 3. Cool before serving.

fields.title: Margherita Pizza
fields.ingredients: Pizza dough, tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, basil.
fields.instructions: 1. Spread sauce on dough. 2. Add cheese and basil. 3. Bake until crispy.

fields.title: Greek Salad
fields.ingredients: Cucumber, tomatoes, olives, feta cheese, red onion, olive oil.
fields.instructions: 1. Toss all ingredients together. 2. Serve chilled.

fields.title: Chicken Alfredo
fields.ingredients: Chicken, fettuccine, Alfredo sauce, Parmesan cheese.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook chicken and fettuccine. 2. Mix with Alfredo sauce. 3. Top with Parmesan.

fields.title: Pancakes
fields.ingredients: Flour, milk, eggs, sugar, baking powder, butter.
fields.instructions: 1. Mix ingredients. 2. Cook on griddle. 3. Serve with syrup.

fields.title: Beef Stroganoff
fields.ingredients: Beef, mushrooms, sour cream, onion, beef broth.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook beef and onions. 2. Add mushrooms and broth. 3. Stir in sour cream and serve.

fields.title: Chicken Caesar Wrap
fields.ingredients: Chicken, Caesar dressing, lettuce, tortilla.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook chicken and mix with Caesar dressing. 2. Place on tortilla with lettuce. 3. Roll up and serve.

fields.title: Quiche Lorraine
fields.ingredients: Pie crust, eggs, cream, bacon, Swiss cheese, onions.
fields.instructions: 1. Pre-bake crust. 2. Mix eggs, cream, cheese, and bacon. 3. Pour into crust and bake.

fields.title: Vegetable Soup
fields.ingredients: Mixed vegetables, vegetable broth, garlic, onions.
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté onions and garlic. 2. Add vegetables and broth. 3. Simmer until vegetables are tender.

fields.title: Tiramisu
fields.ingredients: Mascarpone cheese, coffee, ladyfingers, sugar, cocoa powder.
fields.instructions: 1. Mix mascarpone with sugar. 2. Layer ladyfingers dipped in coffee. 3. Top with mascarpone and cocoa powder.

fields.title: Beef Chili
fields.ingredients: Ground beef, kidney beans, tomatoes, chili powder, onions.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook beef with onions. 2. Add beans, tomatoes, and chili powder. 3. Simmer and serve.

fields.title: Shrimp Scampi
fields.ingredients: Shrimp, garlic, lemon, butter, white wine, parsley.
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté shrimp with garlic and butter. 2. Add lemon juice and wine. 3. Garnish with parsley and serve.

fields.title: Falafel
fields.ingredients: Chickpeas, garlic, onions, cumin, coriander, flour.
fields.instructions: 1. Blend chickpeas with spices and form into balls. 2. Fry until golden brown. 3. Serve with pita and salad.

fields.title: Lemonade
fields.ingredients: Lemons, sugar, water.
fields.instructions: 1. Mix lemon juice with sugar and water. 2. Chill and serve over ice.

fields.title: Chicken Noodle Soup
fields.ingredients: Chicken, noodles, carrots, celery, chicken broth.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook chicken and vegetables. 2. Add broth and noodles. 3. Simmer until noodles are tender.

fields.title: Grilled Cheese Sandwich
fields.ingredients: Bread, cheese, butter.
fields.instructions: 1. Butter bread and add cheese. 2. Grill until golden brown and cheese is melted.

fields.title: Mushroom Risotto
fields.ingredients: Arborio rice, mushrooms, chicken broth, Parmesan cheese, onions.
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté onions and mushrooms. 2. Add rice and broth gradually. 3. Stir in Parmesan and serve.

fields.title: Pesto Pasta
fields.ingredients: Pasta, pesto sauce, Parmesan cheese.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook pasta. 2. Mix with pesto sauce and Parmesan.

fields.title: Apple Pie
fields.ingredients: Apples, sugar, pie crust, cinnamon.
fields.instructions: 1. Fill pie crust with apples and sugar. 2. Top with crust and bake until golden brown.

fields.title: Chicken Parmesan
fields.ingredients: Chicken breasts, marinara sauce, mozzarella cheese, Parmesan cheese.
fields.instructions: 1. Bread and bake chicken. 2. Top with marinara and cheese. 3. Bake until cheese is melted.

fields.title: Tacos
fields.ingredients: Ground beef, taco shells, lettuce, cheese, salsa.
fields.instructions: 1. Cook beef with seasoning. 2. Fill taco shells with beef and toppings.

fields.title: Chocolate Cake
fields.ingredients: Flour, cocoa powder, sugar, eggs, butter.
fields.instructions: 1. Mix ingredients and bake. 2. Cool and frost with chocolate icing.

fields.title: Buffalo Wings
fields.ingredients: Chicken wings, hot sauce, butter, garlic powder.
fields.instructions: 1. Bake or fry wings. 2. Toss with hot sauce and butter.

fields.title: Vegetable Curry
fields.ingredients: Mixed vegetables, curry powder, coconut milk.
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté vegetables with curry powder. 2. Add coconut milk and simmer.

fields.title: S'mores
fields.ingredients: Graham crackers, marshmallows, chocolate.
fields.instructions: 1. Sandwich chocolate and marshmallows between graham crackers. 2. Toast marshmallows and serve.

fields.title: Pork Stir-Fry
fields.ingredients: Pork, bell peppers, soy sauce, garlic, ginger.
fields.instructions: 1. Stir-fry pork with garlic and ginger. 2. Add vegetables and soy sauce.

fields.title: Fried Rice
fields.ingredients: Rice, eggs, vegetables, soy sauce.
fields.instructions: 1. Sauté vegetables and eggs. 2. Add rice and soy sauce.

fields.title: Lasagna
fields.ingredients: Lasagna noodles, ground beef, marinara sauce, cheese.
fields.instructions: 1. Layer noodles with beef, sauce, and cheese. 2. Bake until bubbly.

fields.title: Grilled Salmon
fields.ingredients: Salmon fillets, lemon, olive oil, herbs.
fields.instructions: 1. Marinate salmon in lemon and herbs. 2. Grill until cooked through.

fields.title: Fruit Smoothie
fields.ingredients: Mixed fruits, yogurt, honey.
fields.instructions: 1. Blend fruits with yogurt and honey.
